dct_title_s: Eine Neue Charte von AMERICA Nach den Neusten Observationen
dct_description_sm: In German, with new title: Eine Neue Charte von AMERICA Nach den Neusten Observa- tionen / Von H. Moll Geograph. “(13)” (top right). “Vol. I. Tit Pag. (top left).
Nordenskiöld Collection, 3, Vol.I, 610 (1, State 2); Nordenskiöld Collection, 3, 398 Vol.II (11, State 3); UCB (State 6).
California on second Sanson model, and with "Straits of Annian" and "Mozeemlek" to north; "Gulf of California" to east.
Issued in Das Britische Reich in America ... / John Oldmixon. -- Lemko : bey Johann Heinrich Meyer, 1744.
